dk.aau.cs.d402f13.interpreter

Class SymbolTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • dk.aau.cs.d402f13.interpreter.SymbolTable
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    StandardEnvironment

    public class SymbolTable
extends java.lang.Object
    Symbol table for the interpreter. Keeps track of scopes and all functions, variables, and identifiers existing within all open scopes.
